messages.text: Are you there?
Oh my God, I thought you were dead.
What’s going on??? Where are you??
They drove us to this big building in Easton, called Biotech
It’s set off in the woods a bit off Route 59
I had to pretend I was someone else after it was recognized that I wasn’t the soldier they were expecting.
I’ll get in my car
No, not yet.  I’m not sure if we’re staying here
Is my sister okay??
We got separated when we got here
Where are you now?
I said I had to use the bathroom, then just started scaling the place looking for them
I still haven’t found out who the others girls are, just that they’re in danger and we need to get them out
What kind of danger??
I don’t know, but your sister mouthed “help” to me, as they carted her and the others away
Oh my God…
I should call the cops again
No, don’t do that.
WHY NOT??
I told you, I think they’re in on it somehow
How would they have known where to find the girls if I hadn’t called in the first place?
Maybe it was a coincidence. None of us stuck around to see. Maybe they showed up
Don’t do it. I’m telling you
So then what the hell do we do??
I’ll figure out a plan. First figure out the system, then get around it
Okay. I just…I don’t think I can handle losing her again
You won’t
And we have to be careful even when we get them out...
because I heard someone in the car say something about how they got them from this other group
What does that mean??
That there were some other people trying to smuggle the girls for something too
Are you sure all of them look alike??
Yes!
Did you talk to your parents?
They are acting weird about it
In what way?
They acted excited that she was found, but then went off to the other room to talk privately
I’m here at the house now
And they didn’t try to call the cops to find Adrienne??
No
Don’t you think that’s weird?
I just figured that they thought I called already
Yes, but the last time detectives were all over the place right?
Yeah…
Your parents have to know something
Do you know where they file away important papers? Like your birth certificate?
Yeah.
Go look and see if you can find hers.
What the hell do I do with that??
I don’t know, but it will give some more answers!
As to what??
As to the fact that I think your sister is a science experiment!
What are you saying??
I think she’s a clone…they’ve been doing it on animals and plants for years, why not people?
There were only seven. Septuplets happen
And whatever she is, I want her home safe and we need to figure out how to do that
Security is high, so we’ll have to figure out a way around that.
Oh my God
What??
We definitely have to get them out of here by tonight!
WHAT DID YOU SEE?
I’m standing in a room, where one is being kept
Her brain directly hooked up to monitors, like her skull is open
This is fucking sick
IS IT ADRIENNE??
Anna??
ANNA??
PLEASE ANSWER???
It’s not Adrienne.
And sorry, a doctor came in here and he asked what I was doing.
I told him that I was looking for where the girls are...
that I was a new recruit and needed to do a head count to make sure no others escaped
DID HE TELL YOU??
Yes, I’m on my way there now.
What do I do?? I need to do something!!
Just keep looking through your parents’ papers. After I find them, I’ll come up with a plan
I just found the file for our birth certificates!!
And?
Mine is there. The other is a release form for a place called Lazarus Sciences
I TOLD YOU!
I don’t believe it.
Holy shit…if you saw what I was looking at right now, there would be no other explanation
Did you find them??
Yes. About 40 or 50 of them.
Shit, I have to go…I’ll be in touch
